{"tid":1087493,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"強國人狂搶免費報紙仲放上網炒","createTime":"2019-04-01T11:36:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T11:47:52.000Z","uid":159870,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c198c584ec2d19633df9b0f5b57a92250723a269","tid":1087493,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:36:20.000Z","msg":"香港人又輸了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2745648\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2745648&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c533a56f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2745648&h=76eb7b8e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2745648</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/article?a=20190401-00000066-sasahi-soci\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadlines.yahoo.co.jp%2Farticle%3Fa%3D20190401-00000066-sasahi-soci&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=0b591a77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headlines.yahoo.co.jp/article?a=20190401-00000066-sasahi-soci</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mercari.com/jp/search/?keyword=号外\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mercari.com%2Fjp%2Fsearch%2F%3Fkeyword%3D%E5%8F%B7%E5%A4%96&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=89944f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mercari.com/jp/search/?keyword=号外</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日人推擠爭搶「令和」號外 現場瘋狂傳出怒吼與慘叫<br />\n2019-04-01 16:56<br />\n<br />\n字體Line FB twitter<br />\n今日各大報社於街頭發放號外，竟然引起民眾瘋搶，不少人因推擠而跌在地上，現場甚至傳出怒吼與慘叫。（美聯社）<br />\n今日各大報社於街頭發放號外，竟然引起民眾瘋搶，不少人因推擠而跌在地上，現場甚至傳出怒吼與慘叫。（美聯社）<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕日本政府於今（1）日中午宣布西元645年來第248個年號「令和」，並於5月1日皇太子德仁接棒起正式實施。許多日本人相當關注此消息，今日各大報社於街頭發放號外，竟然引起民眾瘋搶，不少人因推擠而跌在地上，現場甚至傳出怒吼與慘叫。<br />\n據《NHK》報導，各大報社下午1點於東京新橋站前發放號外，竟引來民眾瘋搶，不少人因推擠而跌倒，所有報紙在幾分鐘內全被搶光。一名來自神奈川縣的15歲高中生熱血地表示：「雖然擠得很辛苦，但是可以搶到真的太好了，我會努力在新時代活躍！」；另一名小學2年級的小朋友開心地拿著大人幫他搶來的報紙，天真無邪地表示：「希望新時代可以變成沒有戰爭的和平世界。」<br />\n請繼續往下閱讀...<br />\n<br />\n然而，在JR大阪站前的情況就不只推擠這麼簡單，為了要搶號外，許多人已經在車站外蓄勢待發，警察前往現場維持秩序，呼籲民眾不要擋在路上。但中午號外開始發放後立刻陷入混亂，許多人死命推擠爭搶報紙，現場還傳出怒吼與慘叫，有人只有手能伸進人群中，只搶到已經破掉的其中一角報紙。<br />\n一名順利搶到號外的16歲女同學表示：「人很多很擠，還有人被推倒真的很可怕，但一團混亂下還能搶到真的很開心」。"},{"pid":"b510021d808a12c29eaab2ce308ff5ce5ed685bb","tid":1087493,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XUzq8mV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXUzq8mV.png&h=9c4457d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nd0cOA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nd0cOA.png&h=2eb1ed4c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be43efa8b39515b34bb9e0be22518d0cce63fd4a","tid":1087493,"uid":52611,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:38:11.000Z","msg":"遲下宣傳單張都炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23db76e5555d494242f8a70be4be32daab4aa8c8","tid":1087493,"uid":159870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:41:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://mobile.twitter.com/nhk_news/status/1112601318861012992\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmobile.twitter.com%2Fnhk_news%2Fstatus%2F1112601318861012992&d=kym%2Bu5moN5dZdxbwy4XQi52AEL7eB1GKmMTTK1c2%2F04%3D&h=c4e4893d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://mobile.twitter.com/nhk_news/status/1112601318861012992</a>"},{"pid":"7c0f7b6818c47248dcf79940fee97556a8a37a58","tid":1087493,"uid":4574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:42:02.000Z","msg":"日本都有炒賣師"},{"pid":"30ea92d64f4d76923ae6691daed5804c3da9703a","tid":1087493,"uid":159870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kFUnrb2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkFUnrb2.jpg&h=6a8876cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZK2wjw2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZK2wjw2.jpg&h=40220a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/04/01/194731_896983b4f42f5428b9a41af3fd6a1fe6.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F04%2F01%2F194731_896983b4f42f5428b9a41af3fd6a1fe6.jpeg&h=06d16600&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}